data.chText: 偷偷摸摸的；不声张的；秘密的
data.enText: doing things quietly or secretly; done quietly or secretly

tr: marked by quiet and caution and secrecy
taking pains to avoid being observed
example: a surreptitious glance at his watch

value.def: Stealthy actions or movements are performed quietly and carefully, so that no one will notice what you are doing.

example.ex: I would creep in and with stealthy footsteps explore the second-floor...
example.tran: 我会偷偷溜进去，轻手轻脚地查看一下二楼。

example.ex: It was a stealthy sound made by someone anxious not to be heard.
example.tran: 这是有人不想让别人听到而偷偷摸摸移动的声音。

value.tran: 悄悄的;偷偷摸摸的;鬼鬼祟祟的

example.ex: Slowly and stealthily, someone was creeping up the stairs.
example.tran: 有人正蹑手蹑脚地上楼。
